data.title: List of Songs heard in Movies & TV Shows
data.meta_description: List of all the songs by JO STAFFORD, heard in movies and tv shows. See scene descriptions, listen to their music and download songs.
data.text:
Youth in Revolt2009

The Marvelous Mrs. Maisel  s5e8  The Princess and the Plea2017

Joel and Midge argue in the street when Joel hears the background music. They pause their fight and start dancing.

Agent Carter  s1e1  Now Is Not The End2015

Peggy complains to Angie about her change in job status.

The Walking Dead  s3e7  When the Dead Come Knocking2010

Just before Mr. Coleman turned into a walker

The Marvelous Mrs. Maisel  s4e7  Ethan...Esther...Chaim2017

While driving Ethan to kindergarten, Midge tells about meeting a man at the park.

The Marvelous Mrs. Maisel  s4e7  Ethan...Esther...Chaim2017

The Irishman2019

Song at the club as Frank spots the new waitress, who he ends up marrying.
